          "description": "The floor of the cavern has been scraped clean by the roving inhabitants of the mine. Ancient mining implements of old have cut sheer walls, and the occasional pock mark punctures the shinerock, where the miners checked for further veins of ore. The vast cavern continues to the west, and the shaft of the mine lies to the south.",
