          "vnum": 115,
          "name": "First Tier",
          "description": "Bright, sheer walls line the cavern, mined with methodical precision. Nonetheless, much of the shinerock remains and lights the cavern with its bright radiance. The large cavern of the first tier continues to the east and south, the walls lighting your way as well as any sun.",
