          "description": "Phosphorescent light emanates from the walls of this large cavern, mined into the shinerock. The floor, walls, and ceiling of the first tier are completely bare, scraped clean by the insectoid dwellers of the mine. The shaft of the mine delves deeper into the shinerock to the east. A seam of copper ore glitters with embedded crystalline fragments.",
