          "vnum": 123,
          "name": "Third Tier",
          "description": "Bright walls dazzle your eyes and contract your pupils. Dark shapes move about, easily seen against the light of the glowing rock. The combination of the cold, damp air, and an irritating clicking noise make this place less than relaxing.",
