        "143": {
          "vnum": 143,
          "name": "Cluttered Tunnel",
          "description": "All sorts of things have been strewn across the floor of the tunnel here. Apparently, this is where the insectoid inhabitants bring things that they have scavenged from elsewhere in the mine. Rusted iron mining implements lie decaying in droves upon the tunnel floor. The mess continues to the west. A seam of copper ore glitters with embedded crystalline fragments.",
