        "144": {
          "vnum": 144,
          "name": "Cluttered Tunnel",
          "description": "Rust and rock are the words of choice in this cluttered tunnel. Anything that you might imagine would find its way into a mine has been dragged here by the clickers to clear the rest of the caverns. There's a large mining cart, three pairs of moldy socks, a board with the phrase \"Ghanji's Things\" painted on it, and a complete collector's set of red and white striped pseudo- Napenthian deadly dragon-style wrestling dolls, among other things. The messy tunnel continues to the east, and opens up into a large chamber to the south.",
