        "145": {
          "vnum": 145,
          "name": "Clicker Cavern",
          "description": "A golden shower of light cascades from the glittering shinerock ore in the ceiling far overhead. If this cavern was burrowed by the clickers, it must have taken an awful lot of work, because it's simply massive. The sparkling grandeur of the vast chamber continues to the west and south, and a tunnel filled with junk exits to the north.",
